8 Hours Ago But following the backlash that trailed the tweet, officials of the ministry hurriedly pulled down the post and issued a disclaimer. 


Twitter Reacting to the incident, Special Adviser, Media and Communications to the Minister of Finance, said, “An unauthorised post was made on the verified Twitter handle of the Federal Ministry of Finance, Budget and National Planning. “The fact of the post is regrettable because of which it is brought down. “We have made sure our internal processes are strengthened that such doesn't happen again. The error is highly regrettable.” 